all to the church.

20:25.625 --> 20:27.291
Because she is very religious.

20:27.375 --> 20:29.208
-How nice!
-Another one.

20:29.291 --> 20:33.166
Like my blessed mother,
may she rest in peace. She donated it all.

20:35.250 --> 20:37.541
Sometimes it's really exhausting
to take care of her,

20:37.625 --> 20:39.041
