a space in her house to live.

20:43.291 --> 20:45.208
Well, chocolates to sweeten your life.

20:45.291 --> 20:46.291
Thanks.

20:46.375 --> 20:48.208
-A candle to light it up.
-Oh, how nice!

20:48.291 --> 20:50.208
I made you a cake.
