20:50.291 --> 20:53.416
-but the intention is what counts.
-Oh yeah. How nice!

20:54.083 --> 20:57.583
I brought you an image
of the guardian angel.

20:58.000 --> 20:59.958
-Do you know the pray?
-Of course, yes.

21:00.041 --> 21:02.875
-Angel of God, my guardian dear.
-Angel of God, my guardian dear.

21:03.000 --> 21:04.458
ever this day be at my side
to light and guard,

21:04.541 --> 21:06.208
