21:20.041 --> 21:21.291
Piggy, what snack?

21:21.375 --> 21:24.458
And we were so in love,
we couldn't stop looking at each other.

21:25.500 --> 21:28.333
And two months after we got married,
Alex arrived.

21:28.458 --> 21:30.541
Oh, such blessing.

21:30.791 --> 21:33.333
It is a miracle that the Lord
has brought your paths together.

21:33.416 --> 21:34.666
Where is the lunch box?

21:34.750 --> 21:37.958
Pig, the lunch box has been on
the same shelf for five years, please.

21:38.041 --> 21:39.333
Stop it, Trini.

21:40.083 --> 21:41.791
Excuse me, is that him?

21:42.875 --> 21:44.541
Yes, it's him.

21:44.875 --> 21:47.375
Such tenderness
and what a great sorrow too.

21:48.250 --> 21:50.625
-How long ago did he die?
-Trinidad!

21:50.833 --> 21:52.375
It doesn't matter.
It's ok.

21:52.583 --> 21:54.000
Two years ago already.

21:54.583 --> 21:56.708
He was a fireman,

21:57.166 --> 22:00.291
