with the granny?

22:04.583 --> 22:06.416
Oh, what a sordid question, please!

22:06.500 --> 22:08.458
No, what happens
is that he inhaled toxic gases

22:08.541 --> 22:12.458
and that caused him
a degenerative lung disease.

22:12.750 --> 22:14.666
They gave him six months to live,

22:14.750 --> 22:17.250
but he spent two years fighting.

22:20.250 --> 22:22.833
And he died here, in my arms.

22:26.291 --> 22:28.041
His last words were

22:28.791 --> 22:32.833
"Life will always be too short
with you by my side."

22:34.750 --> 22:36.708
Yeah, but how many meters
did you say the house was?

22:36.791 --> 22:38.208
-Julia.
-No, no, it's just that I was thinking,

22:38.291 --> 22:40.208
the other option
