22:54.291 --> 22:56.166
Yes, a factory in a village.

22:56.958 --> 22:59.958
Factories are the cancer
of the planet.

23:01.166 --> 23:03.000
-And why was the granny in the factory?
-Trinidad.

23:03.083 --> 23:06.250
I don't know. I have no idea,
but if I can tell you something

23:07.541 --> 23:09.666
I miss him every day of my life.

